          </ul>  
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>    
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row" id="next_front_container">
  <div class="container" id="front_hold">
    <div class="container" id="geez_front_hold">
      <div class="row">
       <div class="span7">
          <h3>refreshrunner is ensuring project productivity</h3>
       </div>  
        <a href="#from_the_top" id="no_underline">
          <div id="link_to_signup_section">
            <p>Get things done</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="row top_middle_left_row">
        <div class="top_left span4">
          <div class="span3">
            <h4>Cut the chit chat</h4>
            <p>No comments, file uploads, email threads, or countless meetings. Quickly answer the <button class="btn btn-link custom_btn_link">3 most important questions</button> surrounding any personal or collaborative thing to be done <%= link_to "..more", benefits_path, :class => "more_links"  %></p>
