              </ul>
          </div>
        </div>  
        <div class="top_middle span4">
          <div class="span3">
            <h4>Different planet</h4>
            <p> You will be amazed at how well this workflow will help you get back to the fundamentals of completing meaningful projects. Careful though, because it forces you to be good <%= link_to "..more", benefits_path, :class => "more_links"  %> </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="top_right span4">
          <div class="span3">
            <h4>Take the pressure off you</h4>
            <p>Asking someone for something is worse than pulling teeth. Use refreshrunner and suddenly, it's not me asking you for something, it's you and I trying to pull this tooth out together <%= link_to "..more", benefits_path, :class => "more_links"  %></span>  </p>
          </div>
        </div>  
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row" id="third_front_container">
  <span id="from_the_top"></span>
  <div class="container" id="front_hold">
    <div class="container" id="second_front_hold">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="final_headline">
          <hr>
          <h2>Your free trial starts below.<br> Begin using after the green button.</h2>
          <hr>
        </div>  
      </div>  
         <div class="row">
           <div class="span5 offset1">
            <div id="front_gage" style="height:240px; width:300px;">
            </div>
           </div>  
          <div class="signup_well span4">
            <h4>Get closer to done and sign up below.</h4>
            <div class="row front_signup_lead">
              <p>This form gets you 45-days to try free.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row actual_signup_form">
              <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                <%= devise_error_messages! %>
                <div>
                <%= f.text_field :first_name, :placeholder => "First Name" %></div>
                <div class="first_step">
                <%= f.text_field :last_name, :placeholder => "Last Name" %></div>
                <div class="second_step">
                <%= f.text_field :profile_name, :placeholder => "Profile Name" %></div>
                <div class="second_step">
                <%= f.email_field :email, :placeholder => "Email" %></div>
                <div class="third_step">
                <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => "Password" %></div>
                <div class="third_step">
                <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :placeholder => "Confirm Password" %></div>
                <div id="submit_front_button"><%= f.submit "Get Things Done", :class => "actual_button" %></div>
              <% end %>
            </div>    
            <h5 style="text-align:center;"><small>By signing up you have read and<br> agree to our <%= link_to "terms", terms_path %> and <%= link_to "privacy policy", terms_path %>  </small></h5>
          </div>
         </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <footer class="footer">
    <small class="pull-left">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about" data-toggle="modal">fivefourfooty,</a> 2013</li><br>
        <li><%= link_to image_tag("/assets/twitter.png"), "#twitter", :data => { :toggle =>"modal" } %></li>
        <li><%= link_to image_tag("/assets/facebook.png"), "#facebook", :data => { :toggle =>"modal" } %></li>
